# Ensure consistent line endings for Markdown files.
# This glob already covers every .md in the repo (including those under
# "Unit Testing/" and "Portal Testing/"), so no per-file rules are
# needed. The previous per-file entries pointed at a non-existent cam/
# tree and an unquoted path with a space, which git rejected with
# "not a valid attribute name" on every command.
*.md text eol=lf

